title: S12 Ep152: The Lost Years and Messages of Jesus Christ
itunes:title: The Lost Years and Messages of Jesus Christ
description:
Author/Investigator/Spirit Communicator Barry Strohm uses a spirit board as his main form of communication with "the other side". Barry has connected with people's relatives, famous people, and even people's pets! But, Barry and his wife, Connie, truly got a shock when Popes and Saints started conveying messages about religion and the lost years of Jesus, and they got a huge shock when the man Himself showed up!

Barry Strohm: http://www.spiritspredict.com/
